---
import Button from './ui/Button.astro';
---
<section class="relative py-24 lg:py-48 overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-left bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('/background/bg-kitab-landscape.png');">
  <!-- Subtle White Overlay for readability and Clean Modern Aesthetic -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-[2px]"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight font-aref-ruqaa drop-shadow-sm">
      Pembelajaran Bahasa Arab & Tafsir <br/>
      <span class="text-[#065f46]">by Fuad Rahman</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto drop-shadow-sm">
      Solusi belajar bahasa Arab yang terstruktur dan mudah diakses untuk para santri. Mulailah perjalanan ilmu Anda dengan navigasi yang intuitif.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <Button href="#belajar" variant="primary" class="shadow-emerald-900/10 shadow-xl">
        Mulai Belajar Sekarang
      </Button>
      <Button href="/about" variant="outline">
        Kenali Fuad Rahman
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
